claim: The English Civil War's Parliamentarians were also known as a different name.
premise_source_doc_sentence: `` The English Civil War '' was a series of armed conflicts and political machinations that took place between Parliamentarians and Royalists from 1642 until 1651 , and includes the Second English Civil War  (  1648 -- 1649  )  and the Third English Civil War  (  1649 -- 1651  )  .
